Package com.irurueta.navigation.trilateration

Contains classes to estimate positions when intersecting cirles or spheres by using the trilateration algorithm.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RobustTrilaterationSolverListener<P extends com.irurueta.geometry.Point>
    Listener to be notified of events produced by a robust trilateration solver when solving starts, ends or when progress changes.
    TrilaterationSolverListener<P extends com.irurueta.geometry.Point>
    Listener to be notified of events such as when trilateration solving starts or ends.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LinearLeastSquaresTrilateration2DSolver
    Linearly solves the trilateration problem.
    LinearLeastSquaresTrilateration3DSolver
    Linearly solves the trilateration problem.
    LinearLeastSquaresTrilaterationSolver<P extends com.irurueta.geometry.Point>
    Linearly solves the trilateration problem.
    LMedSRobustTrilateration2DSolver
    Robustly solves the trilateration problem by finding the best pairs of 2D positions and distances among the provided ones using LMedS algorithm to discard outliers.
    LMedSRobustTrilateration3DSolver
    Robustly solves the trilateration problem by finding the best pairs of 3D positions and distances among the provided ones using LMedS algorithm to discard outliers.
    MSACRobustTrilateration2DSolver
    Robustly solves the trilateration problem by finding the best pairs of 2D positions and distances among the provided ones using MSAC algorithm to discard outliers.
    MSACRobustTrilateration3DSolver
    Robustly solves the trilateration problem by finding the best pairs of 3D positions and distances among the provided ones using MSAC algorithm to discard outliers.
    NonLinearLeastSquaresTrilateration2DSolver
    Solves a Trilateration problem with an instance of a least squares optimizer.

    PROSACRobustTrilateration2DSolver
    Robustly solves the trilateration problem by finding the best pairs of 2D positions and distances among the provided ones using PROSAC algorithm to discard outliers.
    PROSACRobustTrilateration3DSolver

    RANSACRobustTrilateration2DSolver

    RANSACRobustTrilateration3DSolver
    Robustly solves the trilateration problem by finding the best pairs of 3D positions and distances among the provided ones using RANSAC algorithm to discard outliers.
    RobustTrilateration2DSolver
    This is an abstract class to robustly solve the trilateration problem by finding the best pairs of 2D positions and distances among the provided ones.
